<item>
            <title>[CXF-5012] Possible regression in the way proxies handle HTTP errors</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-5012</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a proxy can not find a matching HTTP error handler it should throw the exception, 2.7.4 is not handling it correctly&lt;/p&gt;</description>
